{"tid":258184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2男夜總會消遣3粒鐘唔夠錢畀，抵押財物賒數。","createTime":"2017-05-26T01:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T06:05:51.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4679789120d1f9be49a061bb84691258fdaa44","tid":258184,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170526/photo/bkn-20170526070515274-0526_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170526083037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170526070515274-0526_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170526083037&h=07d6e9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2男夜總會跳舞唔夠錢畀，抵押財物賒數。2名年約30歲男子，凌晨1時許，到旺角山東街一間夜總會跳舞消遣，至凌晨4時上址打烊始結賬離開，詎料埋單2千港元，但2人身上僅得1千港元現金，遂取出「EPS」付款，惟碌卡不成功；於是要求用手錶作現金付款，其中一人又聲稱今早出糧後，便返回上址找數，2人擾攘多時，負責人決定報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調停一番，負責人終接受2名事主拿貴重財物抵押，並於今日較後時間，帶夠現款返回上址結帳，雙方始和解，2漢獲准離去。"},{"pid":"56c32f43d53ae8d84b2c398fcf2409046e6340e7","tid":258184,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdd89c35e054ae8627b3929b87f087335e52334","tid":258184,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"賭白頭片"},{"pid":"948cd939a13acd154106ca10f0ffa04b201f37d6","tid":258184,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:29:16.000Z","msg":"其中一人又聲稱今早出糧後，便返回上址找數<br />\n<br />\n1000蚊都要等出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a264e29c4500bb6bc539c890c9845317f15ab1","tid":258184,"uid":10219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:29:51.000Z","msg":"咁撚大個人2k都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6daf4f39d6b6f822556460e56c3570530dacab7","tid":258184,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"真係垃圾來"},{"pid":"a2707180f4812657c29d5427910c78122eb2d19c","tid":258184,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:31:50.000Z","msg":"呢d都叫新聞？"},{"pid":"f1db39e5b68490d62105b19f1bf9815612fe1835","tid":258184,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:32:29.000Z","msg":"EPS 不成功，即係戶口無錢啦<br />\n<br />\n戶口係有錢出去搵提款機撳都得啦"},{"pid":"a6c2c28fdce57b449e4558435476d7becc5a3cee","tid":258184,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>EPS 不成功，即係戶口無錢啦<br />\n<br />\n戶口係有錢出去搵提款機撳都得啦</blockquote><br />\n笑撚死<br />\n應該係明知無錢但又要扮哂野"},{"pid":"683631d44606d22bcdba7c17527276e807f00945","tid":258184,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"係咪九十年代新聞，三十歲人去夜總會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ba3f43541721264c1d7c1e235186ea80f0d11b","tid":258184,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"咁都唔比人打獲金既"},{"pid":"9555f8d148311e6cac4651cd6611a20b3abd042e","tid":258184,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"係咪隔離post個個巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874f00b8e33ea865b714e37c461c74b7cd2fbe9a","tid":258184,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"黑鬥黑"},{"pid":"ca6f8ca8c529aaf6ee7b53aa76e51f0113148645","tid":258184,"uid":99212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"夜總會？"},{"pid":"4f042a6eee753eb38f6295723512767d103effee","tid":258184,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"蔣囝？"},{"pid":"8